<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found | Accela</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="https://files.catbox.moe/bpi1je.gif" type="image/gif">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif;
      background: #0a092d;
      color: #ffffff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    @keyframes rotate {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .error-container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 40px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .error-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    .error-code {
      font-size: 96px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #06b6d4);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
    }

    .error-title {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .error-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 12px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #4f46e5;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #4338ca;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .suggestions {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .suggestions h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .suggestions ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .suggestions li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .suggestions a {
      color: #4f46e5;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .suggestions a:hover {
      color: #6366f1;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .error-container {
        padding: 32px 24px;
        margin: 20px;
      }

      .error-icon {
        font-size: 64px;
      }

      .error-code {
        font-size: 72px;
      }

      .error-title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .error-message {
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .btn-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-icon">üîç</div>
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <h1 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h1>
    <p class="error-message">
      The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved. It might have been deleted or the URL might be incorrect.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Go Home</a>
      <a href="/chapters" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Flashcards</a>
    </div>

    <div class="suggestions">
      <h3>Quick Links</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">üè† Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/chapters">üóÇÔ∏è Flashcards</a></li>
        <li><a href="/notes">üìù Notes</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login">üîê Login</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>